<h1 class='c-primaryTitle s-marginTop1_5 blog-posts-show-header__title'>
How to Invest Your Money: A Beginner’s Guide for 2021
</h1>
<p class='c-subtitle s-marginTop1_5 blog-posts-show-header__subtitle'>
This article will discuss the various ways new investors can dip their toe into the wide range of investment opportunities available to them.
</p>
<hr class='c-divider c-divider--extra_small c-divider--left'>
<div class='s-marginVert1'></div>
<div class="u-displayInlineBlock blog-posts-show-author" data-rc="blog/posts/show/author"><div class="c-avatar c-avatar--mini u-displayInlineBlock js-user_avatar"><img alt="Profile picture of Boris Revsin" title="Boris Revsin" srcset="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small_2x/000/065/863/65863-1549486624-f1a4b4c917ecdf3cf7fc24a7f81a9fbc7960d14e.jpg 2x" src="https://uploads.republic.com/p/users/avatars/small/000/065/863/65863-1549486624-c641a5ccc5933ae048601c24bdb92e8e7df0a725.jpg" /></div>
<span class='u-verticalAlignMiddle'>
<span class='u-colorMuted s-marginLeft0_5'>
By
</span>
<a class="js-tooltip_ajax c-link--inherit js-user_role_radar_investor" data-type="user" data-slug="boris-revsin" href="/@boris-revsin">Boris Revsin</a>
<div class='u-colorGrayB s-marginLeft1 u-displayInlineBlock s-paddingVert0_5 blog-posts-show-author__socials'>
